column1: Baby Barnaby's////I almost always order omelets for breakfast
column2: so I was surprised when I didn't see a single one on the menu.  I went for something different and ordered the corned beef hash with eggs over easy.  It came with potatoes
column5: corned beef and eggs.  The eggs were cooked perfectly
column7: and the potatoes were hot and crispy.  I could have done with about half the amount of potatoes
column8: but overall the meal was wonderful.  The service was a little slow and inattentive
column9: but for a lazy Sunday morning
